Q - You need to migrate a relational database from on-premise to the cloud.
    How would you minimize downtime..?
A - Business Logic - Ensure business continuity during migration.
  - Use tools like AWS DMZ or Azure Data Migration service.
  - Enable continous replication to sync changes during migration.
  - Perform migration during non-peak hours.
  - Validate the database in the cloud before switching production traffic.
 
